# Project Context

- This is ft_transcendence, a 42 School curriculum project
- All code must comply with docs/subject.pdf requirements
- Reference docs folder for project specifications

# Technical Stack

- Django + Django REST Framework backend
- Vanilla HTML/CSS/JavaScript frontend (no frameworks)
- PostgreSQL database via Docker
- Django Channels for WebSocket features
- OAuth 2.0 authentication

# Project Structure

- Django apps go in apps/
- Frontend assets in templates/
- Docker configs in docker/
- Documentation in docs/

# Code Standards

- Follow docs/CONTRIBUTING.md
- Document all changes
- Prefer BEM CSS naming
- Maintain existing architecture

# Development

- Use Makefile commands
- Run in Docker containers
- Migrate database changes
- Collect static files with make static

# Security

- No sensitive data in code
- Secure API keys and secrets
- Follow Django security practices
- Validate and sanitize inputs
